      _routes‚Üź‚ć¨
      :If 0<‚ćīroutes
          _RegisterPair¬®routes    ‚ćĚ each element is ‚äā('METHOD /path' 'handlerName')
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Make0;pairs
