    ‚ąá


    ‚ćĚ _RegisterPair  ‚Äď  parse one route row and append to _routes
    ‚ćĚ   row: ('METHOD /path/‚Ä¶'  'handlerName')
    ‚ćĚ         may be enclosed (from routes,‚Üź‚äā‚Ä¶) or a plain vector
    ‚ąá _RegisterPair row;methodPath;handler;sp;r;pair
      pair‚Üź‚äÉ‚ć£(0=‚ČĘ‚ćīrow)‚äĘrow    ‚ćĚ disclose if scalar-enclosed, leave alone if already a vector
      (methodPath handler)‚Üźpair
